Articles.Content:
I'm wondering if there is a visual que when my time-warp can be changed from x4 to 5-50x. This is mainly on Kerbin.

Edited January 26, 2014 by TimePeriod
If you're above 69070m, you can use full timewarp.
Well, if you look carefully at the timewarp bar on the top left of the screen, Phys-Warp (the 4x warp) only has 4 arrows that can light up. Time-Warp (up to 100000x) has significantly more arrows.
